{"tid":123670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國黑市買賣個人資料猖獗　通話紀錄有價有市","createTime":"2017-02-17T04:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T18:36:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c6b9c210c9808507ba6115fa2fad3d7638f9b8","tid":123670,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"有港豬話羨慕中共國日常應用科技先進！交易唔洗現金！揸部機買乜都得。其實哩D唔係乜嘢高科技。西方都無咁普遍，就係保安問題！<br />\n除共產黨肯肯定經電話知道晒機主過去買過乜，食過乜，和乜嘢人一齊，傾過乜！去過邊樹，影過乜相！有無叫過雞，鴨，鵝！都一覽無遺！個個都被淥光豬！<br />\n<br />\n就算【事無不可對黨言】，有日，銀行資料無晒個陣就過引！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1314004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1314004&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7013958d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1314004&h=2071cf83\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1314004</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-16 HKT 22:41<br />\n在中國，網上黑市買賣個人資料成行成市，在其中一個QQ「起底」群組有1900多個註冊帳號，部分人自稱是追數公司。<br />\n<br />\n央視記者註冊帳號後，有黑市商人向記者發送販賣個人資料的清單，聲稱可憑手機號碼，查到用戶的個人身份、戶籍、婚姻狀況、名下資產、手機通話紀錄等，甚至何時入住哪間酒店都可以查到，並列明價目「童叟無欺」。<br />\n<br />\n記者把同事的電話號碼提供給對方，要求查詢同事的資料，查詢結果詳盡且準確無誤。對方更聲稱可以查到其他關聯信息，包括出入境紀錄、名下汽車和違法犯罪紀錄等。央視記者已向公安報案，調查這些原本應該保存在政府機構、銀行和電訊商等的個人私隱，為何會流入黑市。"},{"pid":"4c6a3e8bccb72f55e6c55ef92cfdeb969ad5b9f6","tid":123670,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522abfb1628eba10bfcfed02f9787ec57f9b4386","tid":123670,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"因為人哋本身就唔介意俾黨監控"},{"pid":"6f0df58a85741c46403e0fcff0e6b9407c57c613","tid":123670,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"之前的post一大堆 人話 羨慕強國去現金化<br />\n話要求現金化<br />\n<br />\n心諗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野是要平衡<br />\n大把義士 就係因為衰 用八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f04e4ba114979c9b3abfe8c155bcb2cb4610ae0","tid":123670,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d97f2f2a4d35903d8099e838bcc7919e21c62e","tid":123670,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"手機台支共電話打手名言：<br />\n你又唔係咩大人物，人地要啲資料托柒咩。<br />\n又唔係做非法野，做咩咁驚比黨知呀？<br />\n香港基站都用華為啦，唔好上網丫笨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17252cba75b51da494450420bb9019f9407e1d8","tid":123670,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"冇「有效機制制衡」實名制嘅副作用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ca88d329c4bda18eea5e24b625e1dfb865d5b2","tid":123670,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"八達通好心7仔買啦冇記名"},{"pid":"ba0e99074834cdd0331e43f463d4414afe5dbd31","tid":123670,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"電子貨幣原本就有利政府監控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27142df75c8ce4555f3cc84fe14d73faa42519d4","tid":123670,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"所以啲咁嘅電子銀包，我一個都無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0684698feb4b54e72ad028903a237b1cd727357b","tid":123670,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八達通好心7仔買啦冇記名</blockquote><br />\n八達通係另一張「身分證」：<br />\n因為同身分證有獨一無二編號，再加上大數據分析，就能搜查到特定人士交易記錄。<br />\n當然，呢D要執法機構，經司法機構發出嘅有效搜查令，才能授權搜查使用電子貨幣嘅特定人士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabfa5d4a4fb10ae3c48205a9601e9aab30fd437","tid":123670,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八達通好心7仔買啦冇記名</blockquote><br />\n八達通係另一張「身分證」：<br />\n因為同身分證有獨一無二編號，再加上大數據分析，就能搜查到特定人士交易記錄。<br />\n當然，呢D要執法機構，經司法機構發出嘅有效搜查令，才能授權搜查使用電子貨幣嘅特定人士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個人八達通<br />\n有名有相有電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d686d38f6b23ad495a0a3633c366a4e69e2a6a09","tid":123670,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}